# Phase 17.4 — Premium Footer Redesign
## Immediate UI Correction Using UI UX Pro Max + 21st.dev

Read and follow all project instructions in the `.claude` folder.

This is an approved design-refinement task.

The current footer is functionally correct but visually unacceptable. It technically satisfies the seven governed content groups, but it presents them as seven narrow, equally weighted columns, producing poor hierarchy, weak branding, excessive visual density, and an unpolished enterprise appearance.

Fix the footer now.

This task explicitly authorises a visual redesign of the footer while preserving the existing CMS, routes, content ownership, legal links, portal access, and navigation governance.

