# Layer 4 — Bottom Bar

Create a clean, compact bottom bar.

Left:

```text
© 2026 The Lylods Group. All rights reserved.
```

Right:

- Privacy Notice
- Cookie Notice
- Accessibility Statement
- Terms of Use

